I"u<h3 id="offsets">Offsets</h3>
<blockquote>
  <p>From the geometric point of view, a surface has no thickness. However, in architecture one often builds with shells. Thus, we need to give our surface model a certain thickness to make it more realistic. 几何角度曲面没有厚度，为了实现出来，需要增加厚度，则需要考虑等距面。</p>
</blockquote>
